#. type: Plain text
#: support/documentation/content/en/documentation/admin/advanced/xmpp_clients.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "The easiest way to do this is to add an SRV record for the \"room\" [subdomain](https://prosody.im/doc/dns#subdomains):\n"
